title: The Food Descriptions Bracket
description: Third month crazy time is back and the KAJ kicks it off with an epic bracket of food description words. First, they take a voicemail about piggy back rides (1:06), then they get into the sweet sixteen (8:00). Later, there's a quick bachelor update (1:07:38), the final four (1:10:28) and a very existential Kool-Aid question (1:15:54).
